# Responsive design

See also: **`accessibility.mdc`**, **`page-layout.mdc`**, **`design-tokens.mdc`**, **`interaction-polish.mdc`**.

Ship for **320px‚Äì375px** first, then scale up. Horizontal overflow on phones is a release blocker.

## Core rule

Every layout and interactive control must **reflow without horizontal scroll** at narrow widths and expose **adequate touch targets** on mobile.

## App shell navigation

**Do not** put unbounded horizontal link rows in the header (`flex` row with 4+ nav items + actions, no wrap, no collapse).

| Viewport | Pattern |
| -------- | ------- |
| `< md` | `Sheet` / hamburger menu, bottom tab bar, or scrollable tabs with fade edge ‚Äî pick one per app |
| `‚â• md` | Full horizontal nav OK |

```tsx
// Bad ‚Äî clips or scrolls horizontally on ~320px
<nav className="flex items-center gap-6">
  <Link>Home</Link><Link>Items</Link><Link>Settings</Link><Button>Sign out</Button>
</nav>

// Good ‚Äî compact shell below md
<nav className="flex items-center justify-between">
  <Sheet><!-- mobile links --></Sheet>
  <div className="hidden md:flex md:gap-6">{/* desktop links */}</div>
</nav>
```

Test at **320px and 375px** before merge (`merge-readiness-check`).

## Touch targets (WCAG 2.5.5)

Minimum **44√ó44 CSS px** hit area for tappable controls on touch devices.

| Control | Pattern |
| ------- | ------- |
| Primary actions | shadcn `Button` (`size="default"` / `size="icon"`) |
| Pager dots, tiny icons | `min-h-11 min-w-11` wrapper with visual dot centered inside ‚Äî not `size-2` alone |
| List remove / icon actions | `Button variant="ghost" size="icon"` ‚Äî not `h-7 w-7` raw `<button>` |

```tsx
// Bad ‚Äî 8px dot is untappable
<button className="size-2 rounded-full bg-muted" />

// Good ‚Äî 44px hit area, small visual indicator
<button type="button" className="flex size-11 items-center justify-center" aria-label="Go to slide 2">
  <span className="size-2 rounded-full bg-primary" aria-hidden />
</button>
```

Prefer **`Button`** over hand-rolled `<button className="h-7 w-7">`.

## Primary CTAs on mobile

Main page actions (Save, Generate, Submit) use **`w-full sm:w-auto`** ‚Äî see `page-layout.mdc` (`PageFooterActions`).

## Layout patterns

- Use **`flex` + `gap-*`** and **`min-w-0`** on flex children that truncate ‚Äî prevents overflow from long text.
- Tables on mobile ‚Üí card list, horizontal scroll **with** visible affordance, or column hiding ‚Äî not clipped columns.
- Modals / sheets: `max-h-[calc(100dvh-‚Ä¶)]` for full-height panels is OK (`design-tokens.mdc` layout exception).

## Breakpoints

Use Tailwind defaults (`sm`, `md`, `lg`) consistently. Hide/show chrome with `hidden md:flex` ‚Äî not JavaScript width checks unless necessary.

## Anti-patterns

```tsx
// Bad ‚Äî fixed multi-column grid on all viewports
<div className="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">

// Good
<div className="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
```

## Checklist

- [ ] No horizontal page scroll at 320px on changed routes.
- [ ] App nav collapses or adapts below `md`.
- [ ] Custom icon buttons meet 44√ó44 hit area (or use shadcn `Button size="icon"`).
- [ ] Pager dots / step indicators are tappable or replaced by Prev/Next on mobile.
- [ ] Long labels truncate with `truncate` + `title` where helpful.
